bio.singa.simulation.model.rules

Class AppliedExpression

  • java.lang.Object
    • bio.singa.simulation.model.rules.AppliedExpression

  • public class AppliedExpression
extends java.lang.Object
    Applied expressions encapsulate formulas in given in String form. Additionally SimulationParameters need to be defined that are substituted into the expression and resolved for their values.
